": "mp4", "width": 1080, "height": 1920, "tbr": 1359.464, "format_note": "DASH video", "container": "mp4_dash", "vcodec": "vp09.00.40.08.00.01.01.01.00", "acodec": "none", "dynamic_range": "SDR", "url": "https://scontent-mia3-3.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m367/AQNKtFMxbQ-M8fzeAjCU6pV3JlixWWsb4WXhNAUTV7_7uRkZzprXZhjHpo3Vx1Mmv0maEUsTG3QOIV8QBPCRaQXfzJAeL7u3EEkEbA4.mp4?_nc_cat=108&_nc_sid=9ca052&_nc_ht=scontent-mia3-3.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=3X-ToYWQorwQ7kNvwFODkAB&%3D%3D&ccb=17-1&_nc_gid=Wc1PxGQB-mx1S-cpM2XVaw&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ss=7a22e&oh=00_Af62lyZP6qnXpaRDSYGY9jfwDDyAfvQ96cAFXEOPVDthvQ&oe=6A1E43C5", "manifest_stream_number": 0, "is_dash_periods": true, "protocol": "https", "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 1359.464, "resolution": "1080x1920", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 6689582, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/142.0.0.0 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "format": "dash-1461450715672850v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by bilawal.ai", "description": "Comment ‘4d’ to get the full replay. I turned on the aviation layer in my 4D god’s eye replay of the Iran strikes. What jumped out is objectively hilarious.\n\nYou can watch the exact minute panic sets in as the airspace shuts down. Pilots literally doing donuts in the sky trying to figure out where the hell to land.\n\n> 3,400+ commercial flights scattering\n> Cascading no-fly zones locking down the Gulf\n> Planes creeping right between the red zones to escape\n\nIt’s one thing to read about a no-fly zone. It’s another to watch thousands of flights simultaneously hit the brakes and get the hell out of dodge.\n\nOpen source data is undefeated. Replayed in WorldView (dropping April).\n\n#ai #osint #3d #futuretech #aviation"